}]', '8595188182010', '8201', 26, '[]', 0, 'EUR', 'https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/rfx/rfsai-62b-sl/share_dokumentace/en/manual_rfsai-xxb-sl.pdf', '', 'https://www.elkoep.com/media/import/Elko/RFx/RFSAI-62B-SL/3D/3d.html', '', 1768998865911, 1768998865911, '/rfsai-62b-sl                                                                                                                                                    rfsai-62b-sl                                                                                                                                                     <p>the switching component with one/two output relays is used to control appliances and lights. switches/buttons connected to the wiring can be used for control.</p><p>they can be combined with detectors, controllers, or inels rf control system components.</p><p>the box-sl version offers installation directly in the installation box, ceiling, or cover of the controlled appliance. easy installation thanks to screwless terminals.</p><p>it allows the connection of switched loads with a total sum of 8 a (2,000 w).</p><p>functions: for rfsai 61b-sl and rfsai 62b-sl - pushbutton, impulse relay, and time functions of a delayed start or return with time setting 2 s-60 min. any function can be assigned to each output relay. for rfsai-11b-sl, the button has a fixed function - on / off.</p><p>the external button is assigned in the same way as the wireless one.</p><p>each of the outputs can be controlled by up to 12/12 channels (1-channel represents one button on the controller). up to 25 channels for rfsai-61b-sl and rfsai-11b-sl.</p><p>the programming button on the component also serves as a manual output control.</p><p>possibility to set the output status memory in case of failure and subsequent power recovery.</p><p>the elements of the repeater can be set for the components via the rfaf / usb service device, pc, or application.</p><p>range up to 200 m (outdoors), in case of insufficient signal between the controller and the device, use the rfrp-20 signal repeater or component with the rfio2 protocol that supports this function.</p><p>communication with bidirectional rfio2 protocol.</p><p>the contact material of the agsno2 relay enables the switching of light ballasts.</p> public visible', 'https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/rfx/rfsai-62b-sl/share_dokumentace/en/datasheet_rfsai-61b-sl,%20rfsai-62b-sl,%20rfsai-11b-sl,%20rfsai-61bpf-sl.pdf', '[{"url":"https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/rfx/rfsai-62b-sl/share_dokumentace/en/ec_declaration_of_conformity_rfsai-62b-sl.pdf"}]');
INSERT INTO products VALUES (138, 'en', 'aKAdizqtztyQJTF_N6bKX', '/rfsf-1b', true, 'dZAfi53HpUN4NVbSQ0g1h', 'RFSF-1B', true, '<p>Monitors areas (e.g. bathrooms, basements, shafts or tanks) to provide flood warning.</p><p>Upon detecting water, the fl ood detector immediately sends a signal to the switched unit, which further switches on a pump, GSM gate or closes a pipe valve.</p><p>The programming button on the detector is used to:<br>a) setting the function with switching unit<br>b) ascertaining battery status<br>c) ascertaining signal quality between the unit and detector.</p><p>Battery power supply (1x 3 V CR 2477 battery - included in the supply) with battery life of around 1 year based on frequency of use.</p><p>The detector can be placed anywhere thanks to battery power.</p><p>Range up to 160 m (in open space); if the signal is insufficient between the controller and unit, use the signal repeater RFRP-20 or protocol component RFIO2, that support this feature.</p><p>Communication frequency with bidirectional protocol RFIO.</p><p>Option of connecting an external probe FP-1, max. wire length 30 m.</p>', true, NULL, '[]', 'product', 1769166000000, '[]', 'RFSF-1B', 'Level switch', '[{"image":{"uploadId":796,"alt":""},"alt":""}]', '8595188148603', '4860', 34, '[]', 0, 'EUR', 'https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/rfx/rfsf-1b/share_dokumentace/en/manual_rfsf-1b.pdf', '', 'https://www.elkoep.com/media/import/Elko/RFx/RFSF-1B/3D/3d.html', '', 1769173036894, 1769173036894, '/rfsf-1b                                                                                                                                                         rfsf-1b                                                                                                                                                          <p>monitors areas (e.g. bathrooms, basements, shafts or tanks) to provide flood warning.</p><p>upon detecting water, the fl ood detector immediately sends a signal to the switched unit, which further switches on a pump, gsm gate or closes a pipe valve.</p><p>the programming button on the detector is used to:<br>a) setting the function with switching unit<br>b) ascertaining battery status<br>c) ascertaining signal quality between the unit and detector.</p><p>battery power supply (1x 3 v cr 2477 battery - included in the supply) with battery life of around 1 year based on frequency of use.</p><p>the detector can be placed anywhere thanks to battery power.</p><p>range up to 160 m (in open space); if the signal is insufficient between the controller and unit, use the signal repeater rfrp-20 or protocol component rfio2, that support this feature.</p><p>communication frequency with bidirectional protocol rfio.</p><p>option of connecting an external probe fp-1, max. wire length 30 m.</p> public visible', 'https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/rfx/rfsf-1b/share_dokumentace/en/datasheet_rfsf-1b.pdf', '[{"url":"https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/rfx/rfsf-1b/share_dokumentace/en/ec_declaration_of_conformity_rfsf-1b.pdf"}]');
INSERT INTO products VALUES (105, 'en', 'eoge23nLHNMip6CFdAMnV', '/rfsa-66m', true, 't3Up1m494Zw6oxXordyMo', 'RFSA-66M', true, '<p>RFSA-66M: the switching unit with 6 output channels 8 A is used for independent control of up to 6 appliances, sockets or lights.<br>- the three-module design of the unit into a switchboard).<br>- each of the channels may be controlled by up to 25 channels.<br>- the package includes an internal antenna AN-I, in case of locating the element in a metal switchboard, you can use the external antenna AN-E for better signal reception</p><p>6 function: button, impulse relay and time function of a delayed start or return with a time setting range of 2 s - 60 min.</p><p>The programming button on the unit is also used for manual control of the output.</p><p>Memory status can be pre-set in the event of a power failure</p>', true, NULL, '[]', 'product', 1768993200000, '[]', 'RFSA-66M', 'Switching units, 6-channels', '[{"image":{"uploadId":767,"alt":""},"alt":""}]', '8595188142823', '7723', 26, '[]', 0, 'EUR', 'https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/rfx/rfsa-66m/share_dokumentace/en/manual_rfsa-6xm_mi.pdf', '', 'https://www.elkoep.com/media/import/Elko/RFx/RFSA-66M/3D/3d.html', '', 1769001916401, 1769002015322, '/rfsa-66m                                                                                                                                                        rfsa-66m                                                                                                                                                         <p>rfsa-66m: the switching unit with 6 output channels 8 a is used for independent control of up to 6 appliances, sockets or lights.<br>- the three-module design of the unit into a switchboard).<br>- each of the channels may be controlled by up to 25 channels.<br>- the package includes an internal antenna an-i, in case of locating the element in a metal switchboard, you can use the external antenna an-e for better signal reception</p><p>6 function: button, impulse relay and time function of a delayed start or return with a time setting range of 2 s - 60 min.</p><p>the programming button on the unit is also used for manual control of the output.</p><p>memory status can be pre-set in the event of a power failure</p> public visible', 'https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/rfx/rfsa-66m/share_dokumentace/en/datasheet_rfsa-66mx.pdf', '[{"url":"https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/rfx/rfsa-66m/share_dokumentace/en/ec_declaration_of_conformity_rfsa-66m_230v.pdf"},{"url":"https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/rfx/rfsa-66m/share_dokumentace/en/ec_declaration_of_conformity_rfsa-66m_24v.pdf"}]');
INSERT INTO products VALUES (109, 'en', 'DuZvg4Pe3nMVZZBgXDtZ1', '/rfsc-61n', true, 'nXQrAv0aHan-1qg6mD2Pf', 'RFSC-61N', true, '<p>The switched socket is used to control fans, lamps, direct heaters, and appliances, which are connected by a power cord with a plug up to 16 A.</p><p>They can be combined with detectors, controllers, or iNELS RF Control system components.</p><p>Multifunctional design - button, impulse relay and time functions of a delayed start or return with time setting 2 s - 60 min.&nbsp;</p><p>The switched socket can be controlled by up to 32 channels.</p><p>The programming button on the socket also serves as a manual output control with indication.</p><p>Possibility to set the output status memory in case of failure and subsequent power recovery.</p><p>Range up to 200 m (outdoors) (in case of insufficient signal between the controller and the device, use the RFRP-20 signal repeater) or components with the RFIO2 protocol that support this function.</p><p>Communication with bidirectional RFIO2 protocol.</p><p>Thanks to the socket design, installation is simple and straightforward by plugging it into an existing socket.</p><p>The contact material of the AgSnO2 relay enables the switching of light ballasts.</p><p><strong>Produced in 3 designs of sockets/plugs:</strong><br>a)&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;French (CZ, SK, PL, FR)<br>b)&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Schuko (HU, DE, RU, AT, RO, ES)<br>c)&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;British (GB)</p>', true, NULL, '[]', 'product', 1768993200000, '[]', 'RFSC-61N', 'Switching socket-plug - multifunction', '[{"image":{"uploadId":757,"alt":""},"alt":""}]', '8595188182515', '8251', 26, '[]', 0, 'EUR', 'https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/rfx/rfsc-61n/share_dokumentace/en/manual_rfsc-61n.pdf', '', 'https://www.elkoep.com/media/import/Elko/RFx/RFSC-61N/3D/3d.html', '', 1769002239626, 1769002239626, '/rfsc-61n                                                                                                                                                        rfsc-61n                                                                                                                                                         <p>the switched socket is used to control fans, lamps, direct heaters, and appliances, which are connected by a power cord with a plug up to 16 a.</p><p>they can be combined with detectors, controllers, or inels rf control system components.</p><p>multifunctional design - button, impulse relay and time functions of a delayed start or return with time setting 2 s - 60 min.&nbsp;</p><p>the switched socket can be controlled by up to 32 channels.</p><p>the programming button on the socket also serves as a manual output control with indication.</p><p>possibility to set the output status memory in case of failure and subsequent power recovery.</p><p>range up to 200 m (outdoors) (in case of insufficient signal between the controller and the device, use the rfrp-20 signal repeater) or components with the rfio2 protocol that support this function.</p><p>communication with bidirectional rfio2 protocol.</p><p>thanks to the socket design, installation is simple and straightforward by plugging it into an existing socket.</p><p>the contact material of the agsno2 relay enables the switching of light ballasts.</p><p><strong>produced in 3 designs of sockets/plugs:</strong><br>a)&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;french (cz, sk, pl, fr)<br>b)&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;schuko (hu, de, ru, at, ro, es)<br>c)&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;british (gb)</p> public visible', 'https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/rfx/rfsc-61n/share_dokumentace/en/datasheet_rfsc-61n.pdf', '[{"url":"https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/rfx/rfsc-61n/share_dokumentace/en/ec_declaration_of_conformity_rfsc-61n.pdf"}]');
INSERT INTO products VALUES (112, 'en', 'owPHjJD2Nxmyp-jPH6WN0', '/rfdali-04b-sl', true, 'IIgBzbPfft-HZLCptyO40', 'RFDALI-04B-SL', true, '<p>The RFDALI-04B-SL converter is designed to control devices with a DALI&nbsp;interface, such as dimmers, electronic ballasts, LED converters, and&nbsp;more.</p><p>The control is performed by components from the iNELS RF Control&nbsp;system, detectors, controllers, or system devices.</p><p>Assignment and configuration of DALI devices are performed via the&nbsp;application via the web interface.</p><p>The DALI bus is powered by the controller.</p><p>Control input “S” for connection and control of wired buttons.</p><p>The programming button on the transmitter also serves as a manual&nbsp;output control.</p><p>Possibility to set memory status in case of power failure.</p><p>The repeater function of the components can be set via the RFAF / USB&nbsp;service device.</p><p>Range up to 200 m (outdoors), in case of insufficient signal between the controller and the device, use the RFRP-20 signal repeater or&nbsp;components with the RFIO2 protocol that support this function.</p><p>The BOX version offers mounting directly in the installation box, ceiling&nbsp;or luminaire cover, and screwless terminals for connection.</p><p>Communication with bidirectional protocol iNELS RF Control2 (RFIO2).</p>', true, NULL, '[]', 'product', 1768993200000, '[]', 'RFDALI-04B-SL', 'DALI converter, 4 addresses', '[{"image":{"uploadId":773,"alt":""},"alt":""}]', '8595188185271', '8527', 27, '[]', 0, 'EUR', 'https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/rfx/rfdali-04b-sl/share_dokumentace/en/manual_rfdali-04b_32b-sl_en-cz.pdf', '', 'https://www.elkoep.com/media/import/Elko/RFx/RFDALI-32B-SL/3D/3d.html', '', 1769002539229, 1769002539229, '/rfdali-04b-sl                                                                                                                                                   rfdali-04b-sl                                                                                                                                                    <p>the rfdali-04b-sl converter is designed to control devices with a dali&nbsp;interface, such as dimmers, electronic ballasts, led converters, and&nbsp;more.</p><p>the control is performed by components from the inels rf control&nbsp;system, detectors, controllers, or system devices.</p><p>assignment and configuration of dali devices are performed via the&nbsp;application via the web interface.</p><p>the dali bus is powered by the controller.</p><p>control input “s” for connection and control of wired buttons.</p><p>the programming button on the transmitter also serves as a manual&nbsp;output control.</p><p>possibility to set memory status in case of power failure.</p><p>the repeater function of the components can be set via the rfaf / usb&nbsp;service device.</p><p>range up to 200 m (outdoors), in case of insufficient signal between the controller and the device, use the rfrp-20 signal repeater or&nbsp;components with the rfio2 protocol that support this function.</p><p>the box version offers mounting directly in the installation box, ceiling&nbsp;or luminaire cover, and screwless terminals for connection.</p><p>communication with bidirectional protocol inels rf control2 (rfio2).</p> public visible', 'https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/rfx/rfdali-04b-sl/share_dokumentace/en/datasheet_rfdali-04b_32b-sl.pdf', '[{"url":"https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/rfx/rfdali-04b-sl/share_dokumentace/en/ec_declaration_of_conformity_rfdali-04b-sl.pdf"}]');
INSERT INTO products VALUES (113, 'en', 'hLbD8pvAQgQN-TPTLl9vF', '/rfdel-71b-sl', true, 'tUM-OYlZEqKFxX_Y3FVa_', 'RFDEL-71B-SL', true, '<p>Universal built-in dimmer is used to regulate light sources:</p><p>R – classic light bulbs,</p><p>L – halogen bulbs with wound transformer,</p><p>C – halogen bulbs with electronic transformer,</p><p>ESL – dimmable energy saving lamps,</p><p>LED – LED light sources (230 V).</p><p>They can be combined with Detectors, Controllers, or iNELS RF Control&nbsp;System Elements.</p><p>7 light functions - smooth start or stop with time setting 2 s-30 min.</p><p>Min. brightness eliminates flickering LED and ESL light sources.</p><p>The universal dimmer can be controlled by up to 25 channels</p><p>Control input “S” for connecting an existing wired button.</p><p>The programming button on the device also serves as a manual output&nbsp;control.</p><p>Possibility to set memory status in case of power failure.</p><p>The repeater function of the components can be set via the RFAF / USB&nbsp;service device.</p><p>Range up to 200 m (outdoors), in case of insufficient signal between&nbsp;the controller and the component, use the RFRP-20 signal repeater or&nbsp;components with the RFIO2 protocol that support this function.</p><p>The BOX version offers to mount directly in the installation box, ceiling, or luminaire cover.</p><p>Communication with bidirectional protocol iNELS RF Control2 (RFIO2).</p>', true, NULL, '[]', 'product', 1768993200000, '[]', 'RFDEL-71B-SL', 'Universal dimmer, 1-channel', '[{"image":{"uploadId":772,"alt":""},"alt":""}]', '8595188183611', '8361', 27, '[]', 0, 'EUR', 'https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/rfx/rfdel-71b-sl/share_dokumentace/en/manual_rfdel-71b-sl.pdf', '', 'https://www.elkoep.com/media/import/Elko/RFx/RFDEL-71B-SL/3D/3d.html', '', 1769002611911, 1769002611911, '/rfdel-71b-sl                                                                                                                                                    rfdel-71b-sl                                                                                                                                                     <p>universal built-in dimmer is used to regulate light sources:</p><p>r – classic light bulbs,</p><p>l – halogen bulbs with wound transformer,</p><p>c – halogen bulbs with electronic transformer,</p><p>esl – dimmable energy saving lamps,</p><p>led – led light sources (230 v).</p><p>they can be combined with detectors, controllers, or inels rf control&nbsp;system elements.</p><p>7 light functions - smooth start or stop with time setting 2 s-30 min.</p><p>min. brightness eliminates flickering led and esl light sources.</p><p>the universal dimmer can be controlled by up to 25 channels</p><p>control input “s” for connecting an existing wired button.</p><p>the programming button on the device also serves as a manual output&nbsp;control.</p><p>possibility to set memory status in case of power failure.</p><p>the repeater function of the components can be set via the rfaf / usb&nbsp;service device.</p><p>range up to 200 m (outdoors), in case of insufficient signal between&nbsp;the controller and the component, use the rfrp-20 signal repeater or&nbsp;components with the rfio2 protocol that support this function.</p><p>the box version offers to mount directly in the installation box, ceiling, or luminaire cover.</p><p>communication with bidirectional protocol inels rf control2 (rfio2).</p> public visible', 'https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/rfx/rfdel-71b-sl/share_dokumentace/en/datasheet_rfdel-71b-sl.pdf', '[]');
INSERT INTO products VALUES (121, 'en', 'ySrOLb4tSoSpiUNkzAgQS', '/rftc-7', true, 'mIiWA-5ZF-akdv4z6G-fy', 'RFTC-7', true, '<p>Designed for controlling RFSTI-11B, RFATV-2 thermovalve, RF switching&nbsp;elements. Configuration is done in the web browser and also using&nbsp;iNELS APP</p><p>Built-in digital temperature and humidity sensor</p><p>It allows control of diff erent heating sources in up to 16 independent&nbsp;zones (rooms)</p><p>WiFi for parameter setting (via web browser) and for connection to&nbsp;iNELS.Cloud, iNELS APP</p><p>iNELS RFIO2 for wireless communication with iNELS Wireless units</p><p>Power supply: USB-C 5 V</p><p>Black or white glass design</p><p>Box allows mounting on EU/BS installation boxes with 60 mm screw&nbsp;spacing. The stand can be used for easy installation</p>', true, NULL, '[]', 'product', 1769166000000, '[]', 'RFTC-7', 'Smart glass multi-zone thermostat', '[{"image":{"uploadId":783,"alt":""},"alt":""}]', '8595188194174', '9417 standard', 29, '[]', 0, 'EUR', 'https://youtu.be/627j6xEY0lY', 'https://youtu.be/cndRWlYwvC4', '', '', 1769160724281, 1769160724281, '/rftc-7                                                                                                                                                          rftc-7                                                                                                                                                           <p>designed for controlling rfsti-11b, rfatv-2 thermovalve, rf switching&nbsp;elements. configuration is done in the web browser and also using&nbsp;inels app</p><p>built-in digital temperature and humidity sensor</p><p>it allows control of diff erent heating sources in up to 16 independent&nbsp;zones (rooms)</p><p>wifi for parameter setting (via web browser) and for connection to&nbsp;inels.cloud, inels app</p><p>inels rfio2 for wireless communication with inels wireless units</p><p>power supply: usb-c 5 v</p><p>black or white glass design</p><p>box allows mounting on eu/bs installation boxes with 60 mm screw&nbsp;spacing. the stand can be used for easy installation</p> public visible', '', '[{"url":"https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/rfx/rftc-7/share_dokumentace/en/ec_declaration_of_conformity_rftc-7.pdf"}]');
INSERT INTO products VALUES (139, 'en', 'ukE9zP8Z-4YSTs_0V0KYg', '/elan-204', true, 'vx1C6eIjHbQewaE67Vg_v', 'eLAN-204', true, '<p>The smart gateway enables control of iNELS Wireless and iNELS&nbsp;Home components from applications (smartphones, tablets, voice&nbsp;assistants) and other third-party devices using MQTT communication.</p><p>Up to 70 iNELS Wireless devices or 20 iNELS Home devices can be&nbsp;connected, and it processes set programs for automatic control, time&nbsp;scenarios, or schedules for heating control.</p><p>Thanks to two-way communication, it displays the current status of&nbsp;individual elements and sends push notifications about their status.</p><p>It provides a connection to the iNELS Cloud for remote control without&nbsp;the need for a static IP or advanced automation settings.</p><p>It can be placed anywhere on a horizontal surface, and thanks to its&nbsp;flat surface and removable base, it can also be mounted on a wall or&nbsp;ceiling.</p><p>Powered by a 5 V DC/2 A adapter, USB-C connector (included).</p>', true, NULL, '[]', 'product', 1769166000000, '[]', 'eLAN-204', 'Smart gateway', '[{"image":{"uploadId":803,"alt":""},"alt":""}]', '8595188193573', '9357', 35, '[]', 0, 'EUR', 'https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/elan/elan-204/share_dokumentace/en/manual_elan-204_9q.pdf', '', '', '', 1769173428405, 1769173428405, '/elan-204                                                                                                                                                        elan-204                                                                                                                                                         <p>the smart gateway enables control of inels wireless and inels&nbsp;home components from applications (smartphones, tablets, voice&nbsp;assistants) and other third-party devices using mqtt communication.</p><p>up to 70 inels wireless devices or 20 inels home devices can be&nbsp;connected, and it processes set programs for automatic control, time&nbsp;scenarios, or schedules for heating control.</p><p>thanks to two-way communication, it displays the current status of&nbsp;individual elements and sends push notifications about their status.</p><p>it provides a connection to the inels cloud for remote control without&nbsp;the need for a static ip or advanced automation settings.</p><p>it can be placed anywhere on a horizontal surface, and thanks to its&nbsp;flat surface and removable base, it can also be mounted on a wall or&nbsp;ceiling.</p><p>powered by a 5 v dc/2 a adapter, usb-c connector (included).</p> public visible', 'https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/elan/elan-204/share_dokumentace/en/datasheet_elan-204.pdf', '[{"url":"https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/elan/elan-204/share_dokumentace/en/ec_declaration_of_conformity_elan-204.pdf"}]');
INSERT INTO products VALUES (114, 'en', '2jPNbxdalhRBg3W9v97ME', '/rfdsc-71n', true, '5T17YE9_gTCOifym4LPbq', 'RFDSC-71N', true, '<p>The dimmable socket is used to control the brightness of luminaires that are connected by a power cord with a plug:</p><p>R - conventional bulbs (resistive load)</p><p>L - halogen bulbs with winding transformer (inductive load)</p><p>C - halogen bulbs with electronic transformer (capacitive load)</p><p>ESL - dimmable energy-saving lamps</p><p>LED - light sources equipped with LEDs</p><p>Multifunction - 6 light functions - smooth start or stop with time setting 2 s - 30 min. Description of functions on page 73.</p><p>Min. brightness potentiometer eliminates flickering of LED and ESL light sources.</p><p>The universal dimmer can be controlled by up to 32 channels.</p><p>The programming button on the socket also serves as a manual output control.</p><p>Possibility to set the output status memory in case of failure and subsequent power recovery.</p><p>Range up to 160 m (outdoors), in case of insufficient signal between the controller and the device, use the RFRP-20 signal repeater or components with the RFIO2 protocol that support this function.</p><p>Communication with bidirectional RFIO2 protocol.</p><p><strong>Available in 3 socket and plug designs:</strong></p><p>(a) French (CZ, SK, PL, FR)<br>b) Schuko (HU, DE, RU, AT, RO, ES)<br>c) British (GB)</p>', true, NULL, '[]', 'product', 1768993200000, '[]', 'RFDSC-71N', 'Dimming socket-plug', '[{"image":{"uploadId":771,"alt":""},"alt":""}]', '8595188183598', '8359', 27, '[]', 0, 'EUR', 'https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/rfx/rfdsc-71n/share_dokumentace/en/manual_rfdsc-71n.pdf', '', 'https://www.elkoep.com/media/import/Elko/RFx/RFDSC-71N/3D/3d.html', '', 1769002679457, 1769002679457, '/rfdsc-71n                                                                                                                                                       rfdsc-71n                                                                                                                                                        <p>the dimmable socket is used to control the brightness of luminaires that are connected by a power cord with a plug:</p><p>r - conventional bulbs (resistive load)</p><p>l - halogen bulbs with winding transformer (inductive load)</p><p>c - halogen bulbs with electronic transformer (capacitive load)</p><p>esl - dimmable energy-saving lamps</p><p>led - light sources equipped with leds</p><p>multifunction - 6 light functions - smooth start or stop with time setting 2 s - 30 min. description of functions on page 73.</p><p>min. brightness potentiometer eliminates flickering of led and esl light sources.</p><p>the universal dimmer can be controlled by up to 32 channels.</p><p>the programming button on the socket also serves as a manual output control.</p><p>possibility to set the output status memory in case of failure and subsequent power recovery.</p><p>range up to 160 m (outdoors), in case of insufficient signal between the controller and the device, use the rfrp-20 signal repeater or components with the rfio2 protocol that support this function.</p><p>communication with bidirectional rfio2 protocol.</p><p><strong>available in 3 socket and plug designs:</strong></p><p>(a) french (cz, sk, pl, fr)<br>b) schuko (hu, de, ru, at, ro, es)<br>c) british (gb)</p> public visible', 'https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/rfx/rfdsc-71n/share_dokumentace/en/datasheet_rfdsc-71n.pdf', '[{"url":"https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/rfx/rfdsc-71n/share_dokumentace/en/ec_declaration_of_conformity_rfdsc-71n.pdf"}]');
INSERT INTO products VALUES (115, 'en', '4LOjSPwm1K84xCvtylSEm', '/rfdel-76m', true, 'P3nKn-2g9DlZoxM2OEOx3', 'RFDEL-76M', true, '<p>The RFDEL-76M is a universal six-channel dimmer that is used to control the brightness intensity of dimmable R - L - C - ESL - LED sources.</p><p>The maximum possible load is 150 VA for 230 V and 75 VA for 120 V for each channel.</p><p>Individual dimmer channels can be connected in parallel to increase the maximum output load at the expense of the number of outputs.</p><p>Each of the output channels is independently controllable and addressable.</p><p>The min. brightness setting eliminates flickering of different types of light sources, the min. brightness and load typesetting are done by PRG buttons.</p><p>Electronic over-current, thermal and short circuit protection that shuts down the output.</p><p>6 galvanically isolated inputs for wired buttons that can be used to control outputs independently of RF.</p><p>Communication with bidirectional RFIO2 protocol. Internal AN-I antenna included, if the element is placed in a metal cabinet, an external AN-E antenna can be used to improve the signal.</p>', true, NULL, '[]', 'product', 1768993200000, '[]', 'RFDEL-76M', 'Universal dimmer, 6-channels', '[{"image":{"uploadId":774,"alt":""},"alt":""}]', '8595188182058', '8205', 27, '[]', 0, 'EUR', 'https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/rfx/rfdel-76m/share_dokumentace/en/manual_rfdel-76m.pdf', '', 'https://www.elkoep.com/media/import/Elko/RFx/RFDEL-76M/3D/3d.html', '', 1769002745294, 1769002767414, '/rfdel-76m                                                                                                                                                       rfdel-76m                                                                                                                                                        <p>the rfdel-76m is a universal six-channel dimmer that is used to control the brightness intensity of dimmable r - l - c - esl - led sources.</p><p>the maximum possible load is 150 va for 230 v and 75 va for 120 v for each channel.</p><p>individual dimmer channels can be connected in parallel to increase the maximum output load at the expense of the number of outputs.</p><p>each of the output channels is independently controllable and addressable.</p><p>the min. brightness setting eliminates flickering of different types of light sources, the min. brightness and load typesetting are done by prg buttons.</p><p>electronic over-current, thermal and short circuit protection that shuts down the output.</p><p>6 galvanically isolated inputs for wired buttons that can be used to control outputs independently of rf.</p><p>communication with bidirectional rfio2 protocol. internal an-i antenna included, if the element is placed in a metal cabinet, an external an-e antenna can be used to improve the signal.</p> public visible', 'https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/rfx/rfdel-76m/share_dokumentace/en/datasheet_rfdel-76m.pdf', '[{"url":"https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/rfx/rfdel-76m/share_dokumentace/en/ec_declaration_of_conformity_rfdel-76m.pdf"}]');
INSERT INTO products VALUES (140, 'en', 'qUD2hEjgN5Py6dVT_krvd', '/rfrp-20n', true, 'JZTCEOHlL3u0Uf5_u1IYG', 'RFRP-20N', true, '<p>The signal repeater is used to increase the range between the&nbsp;controller and the device by up to 200 meters.</p><p>It is designed for signal transmission of up to 20 components.</p><p>Indications:</p><p>green LED - supply voltage,</p><p>red LED - active status (receiving and transmitting RF signal).</p><p>Programming is done with the key.</p><p>Communication frequency with bidirectional RFIO protocol.</p><p>Thanks to the socket design, installation is simple by plugging it&nbsp;directly into the existing socket, the function of the through socket will be retained.</p><p>Produced in 3 designs of sockets/plugs:&nbsp;</p><p>French (CZ, SK, PL, FR)</p><p>Schuko (HU, DE, RU, AT, RO, ES)</p><p>British (GB)</p>', true, NULL, '[]', 'product', 1769166000000, '[]', 'RFRP-20N', 'Repeater to extend the range', '[{"image":{"uploadId":802,"alt":""},"alt":""}]', '8595188145107', '8423 (French)', 35, '[]', 0, 'EUR', 'https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/rfx/rfrp-20n/share_dokumentace/en/manual_rfrp-20n.pdf', '', '', '', 1769173561555, 1769173561555, '/rfrp-20n                                                                                                                                                        rfrp-20n                                                                                                                                                         <p>the signal repeater is used to increase the range between the&nbsp;controller and the device by up to 200 meters.</p><p>it is designed for signal transmission of up to 20 components.</p><p>indications:</p><p>green led - supply voltage,</p><p>red led - active status (receiving and transmitting rf signal).</p><p>programming is done with the key.</p><p>communication frequency with bidirectional rfio protocol.</p><p>thanks to the socket design, installation is simple by plugging it&nbsp;directly into the existing socket, the function of the through socket will be retained.</p><p>produced in 3 designs of sockets/plugs:&nbsp;</p><p>french (cz, sk, pl, fr)</p><p>schuko (hu, de, ru, at, ro, es)</p><p>british (gb)</p> public visible', 'https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/rfx/rfrp-20n/share_dokumentace/en/datasheet_rfrp-20n.pdf', '[{"url":"https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/rfx/rfrp-20n/share_dokumentace/en/ec_declaration_of_conformity_rfrp-20n.pdf"}]');
INSERT INTO products VALUES (116, 'en', '4L4i2RjqBAi6V4BZJPZ5T', '/rfda-73mrgb', true, 'HCDSe9sP1vtpaYsDHPfFf', 'RFDA-73M/RGB', true, '<p>The dimmer for LED strips is used for independent control of 3 single-color&nbsp;LED strips or one RGB LED strip.</p><p>The expanded selection of control modes enables it to be combined with:</p><p>a) detectors, controllers, and system units iNELS RF Control</p><p>b) device with output signal 0 (1)–10 V</p><p>c) potentiometer.</p><p>The unit‘s 3-MODULE design with switchboard mounting enables connection&nbsp;of dimmed load 3x 5 A, which represents:</p><p>a) single-color LED strip 7.2 W – 3x 8 m</p><p>b) RGB LED strip 14.2 W–10 m.</p><p>6 light functions – smooth increase or decrease with time setting&nbsp;2 s – 30 min.</p><p>The dimmer may be controlled by up to 32 channels.</p><p>The power supply of the unit is in the range of 12–24 V DC and is indicated&nbsp;by a green LED.</p><p>The package includes an internal antenna AN-I, in case of locating the&nbsp;unit in a metal switchboard, you can use the external antenna AN-E for&nbsp;better signal reception</p><p>Memory status can be pre-set in the event of a power failure.</p><p>Range up to 160 m (in open space), if the signal is insufficient between&nbsp;the controller and unit, use the signal repeater RFRP-20 or protocol&nbsp;component RFIO2 that supports this feature.</p><p>Communication frequency with bidirectional protocol RFIO2.</p>', true, NULL, '[]', 'product', 1768950000000, '[]', 'RFDA-73M/RGB', 'Dimming actuator for LED (RGB) strips, 3-channels', '[{"image":{"uploadId":775,"alt":""},"alt":""}]', '8595188146814', '4916', 27, '[]', 0, 'EUR', 'https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/rfx/rfda-73m/share_dokumentace/en/manual_rfda-73m.pdf', '', 'https://www.elkoep.com/media/import/Elko/RFx/RFDA-73M/3D/3d.html', '', 1769002843887, 1769002843887, '/rfda-73mrgb                                                                                                                                                     rfda-73m/rgb                                                                                                                                                     <p>the dimmer for led strips is used for independent control of 3 single-color&nbsp;led strips or one rgb led strip.</p><p>the expanded selection of control modes enables it to be combined with:</p><p>a) detectors, controllers, and system units inels rf control</p><p>b) device with output signal 0 (1)–10 v</p><p>c) potentiometer.</p><p>the unit‘s 3-module design with switchboard mounting enables connection&nbsp;of dimmed load 3x 5 a, which represents:</p><p>a) single-color led strip 7.2 w – 3x 8 m</p><p>b) rgb led strip 14.2 w–10 m.</p><p>6 light functions – smooth increase or decrease with time setting&nbsp;2 s – 30 min.</p><p>the dimmer may be controlled by up to 32 channels.</p><p>the power supply of the unit is in the range of 12–24 v dc and is indicated&nbsp;by a green led.</p><p>the package includes an internal antenna an-i, in case of locating the&nbsp;unit in a metal switchboard, you can use the external antenna an-e for&nbsp;better signal reception</p><p>memory status can be pre-set in the event of a power failure.</p><p>range up to 160 m (in open space), if the signal is insufficient between&nbsp;the controller and unit, use the signal repeater rfrp-20 or protocol&nbsp;component rfio2 that supports this feature.</p><p>communication frequency with bidirectional protocol rfio2.</p> public visible', 'https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/rfx/rfda-73m/share_dokumentace/en/datasheet_rfda-73m_rgb.pdf', '[{"url":"https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/rfx/rfda-73m/share_dokumentace/en/ec_declaration_of_conformity_rfda-73m_rgb.pdf"}]');
INSERT INTO products VALUES (117, 'en', 'PYAnmCf96RKSrbRutVHFY', '/rfdel-71m', true, 'onIJUAEA_jVo9BDDH2Ri_', 'RFDEL-71M', true, '<p>The universal modular dimmer is used to regulate light sources:</p><p>R – classic lamps (resistive load)</p><p>L – halogen lamps with wound transformer (inductive load)</p><p>C – halogen lamps with electronic transformer (capacity load)</p><p>ESL – dimmable energy-efficient fluorescent lamps</p><p>LED – LED light sources equiped with LED</p><p>Control can be performed by:</p><p>a) detectors, Controllers and System units iNELS RF Control</p><p>b) by control signal 0(1)–10 V</p><p>c) potentiometer</p><p>d) existing button in the installation.</p><p>6 light functions – smooth increase or decrease with time setting&nbsp;2 s–30 min.&nbsp;</p><p>Thanks for setting the min. brightness by potentiometer, you will eliminate&nbsp;flashing of the LED and ESL light sources.</p><p>The universal dimmer may be controlled by up to 32 channels.</p><p>The programming button on the controller is also used for manual&nbsp;control of the output.</p><p>The package includes an internal antenna AN-I, in case of locating the&nbsp;unit in a metal switchboard, you can use the external antenna AN-E for better signal reception</p><p>Memory status can be pre-set in the event of a power failure.</p><p>Range up to 160 m (in open space), if the signal is insufficient between&nbsp;the controller and unit, use the signal repeater RFRP-20 or protocol&nbsp;component RFIO2 that support this feature.</p><p>Communication frequency with bidirectional protocol RFIO2.</p><p>The unit‘s 3-MODULE design with switchboard mounting.</p>', true, NULL, '[]', 'product', 1768993200000, '[]', 'RFDEL-71M', 'Universal dimmer, 1-channel', '[{"image":{"uploadId":776,"alt":""},"alt":""}]', '8595188148979', '4897', 27, '[]', 0, 'EUR', 'https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/rfx/rfdel-71m/share_dokumentace/en/manual_rfdel-71m.pdf', '', 'https://www.elkoep.com/media/import/Elko/RFx/RFDEL-71M/3D/3d.html', '', 1769002948316, 1769002948316, '/rfdel-71m                                                                                                                                                       rfdel-71m                                                                                                                                                        <p>the universal modular dimmer is used to regulate light sources:</p><p>r – classic lamps (resistive load)</p><p>l – halogen lamps with wound transformer (inductive load)</p><p>c – halogen lamps with electronic transformer (capacity load)</p><p>esl – dimmable energy-efficient fluorescent lamps</p><p>led – led light sources equiped with led</p><p>control can be performed by:</p><p>a) detectors, controllers and system units inels rf control</p><p>b) by control signal 0(1)–10 v</p><p>c) potentiometer</p><p>d) existing button in the installation.</p><p>6 light functions – smooth increase or decrease with time setting&nbsp;2 s–30 min.&nbsp;</p><p>thanks for setting the min. brightness by potentiometer, you will eliminate&nbsp;flashing of the led and esl light sources.</p><p>the universal dimmer may be controlled by up to 32 channels.</p><p>the programming button on the controller is also used for manual&nbsp;control of the output.</p><p>the package includes an internal antenna an-i, in case of locating the&nbsp;unit in a metal switchboard, you can use the external antenna an-e for better signal reception</p><p>memory status can be pre-set in the event of a power failure.</p><p>range up to 160 m (in open space), if the signal is insufficient between&nbsp;the controller and unit, use the signal repeater rfrp-20 or protocol&nbsp;component rfio2 that support this feature.</p><p>communication frequency with bidirectional protocol rfio2.</p><p>the unit‘s 3-module design with switchboard mounting.</p> public visible', 'https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/rfx/rfdel-71m/share_dokumentace/en/datasheet_rfdel-71m.pdf', '[{"url":"https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/rfx/rfdel-71m/share_dokumentace/en/ec_declaration_of_conformity_rfdel-71m_230v.pdf"}]');
INSERT INTO products VALUES (119, 'en', 'eSZo4mjLHv4j0T3Cxve-d', '/rftc-4', true, 'od42ot3446HgJxhUYq6jq', 'RFTC-4', true, '<p>Designed to control RFSTI-11B, RFSA-266M</p><p>Built-in digital temperature and humidity sensor</p><p>VA/TN LCD display, 8 touch backlight buttons</p><p>WiFi for parameter setting (via web browser) and for connection to&nbsp;iNELS.Cloud, iNELS APP only with external power supply</p><p>iNELS RFIO2 for wireless communication with iNELS Wireless units</p><p>Power supply: 2x AA 1.5 V or USB-C 5 V</p><p>Black or white glass design</p><p>Box for mounting on EU/BS installation boxes with 60 mm screw spacing&nbsp;</p><p>6 thermostat buttons, 2 buttons options for control switch units, dimmers or switch units for blinds from iNELS Wireless portfolio</p><p>Possibility of custom tuning and design modifi cations (button functions,&nbsp;icon options, logos): icons.inels.com</p>', true, NULL, '[]', 'product', 1769166000000, '[]', 'RFTC-4', 'Smart glass thermostat, battery powered', '[{"image":{"uploadId":780,"alt":""},"alt":""}]', '8595188189170', '8917', 29, '[]', 0, 'EUR', '', 'https://youtu.be/dHQp4ptfSoI', '', '', 1769160553492, 1769160553492, '/rftc-4                                                                                                                                                          rftc-4                                                                                                                                                           <p>designed to control rfsti-11b, rfsa-266m</p><p>built-in digital temperature and humidity sensor</p><p>va/tn lcd display, 8 touch backlight buttons</p><p>wifi for parameter setting (via web browser) and for connection to&nbsp;inels.cloud, inels app only with external power supply</p><p>inels rfio2 for wireless communication with inels wireless units</p><p>power supply: 2x aa 1.5 v or usb-c 5 v</p><p>black or white glass design</p><p>box for mounting on eu/bs installation boxes with 60 mm screw spacing&nbsp;</p><p>6 thermostat buttons, 2 buttons options for control switch units, dimmers or switch units for blinds from inels wireless portfolio</p><p>possibility of custom tuning and design modifi cations (button functions,&nbsp;icon options, logos): icons.inels.com</p> public visible', 'https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/rfx/rftc-4/share_dokumentace/en/datasheet_rftc-4.pdf', '[{"url":"https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/rfx/rftc-4/share_dokumentace/en/ec_declaration_of_conformity_rftc-4.pdf"}]');
INSERT INTO products VALUES (123, 'en', 'kXoJ_aMhRg7qOh48AFpPy', '/rftc-50g', true, 'P7-0HnrK5wdlkLrrD6C1a', 'RFTC-50/G', true, '<p>RFTC-50/G is a separate thermostat that allows wireless control of up to 4 multifunctional switching components, e.g. RFSA-6x, RFUS-61, RFSTI-11B-SL.</p><p>Temperature measurement with the built-in sensor in the range of 0.55 ° C, temperature setting in the range of 0 to + 55 ° C in the weekly program.</p><p>The backlit LCD display displays the current and set temperature, status (ON/OFF), battery status, day of the week, current time, etc.</p><p>Battery power (2x 1.5 V AAA batteries - included in supply) with a battery life of around 1 year based on the frequency of use.</p><p>Range up to 100 m (in open space), if the signal is insufficient between the controller and unit, use the signal repeater RFRP-20 or protocol component RFIO2 that supports this feature.</p><p>Communication frequency with bidirectional protocol RFIO.</p><p>Color combination of temperature unit in design of frames LOGUS90 (plastic, glass, wood, metal, stone).</p>', true, NULL, '[]', 'product', 1769166000000, '[]', 'RFTC-50/G', 'Autonomous temperature controller', '[{"image":{"uploadId":785,"alt":""},"alt":""}]', '8595188148641', 'RFTC-50/G/BR/BR standard', 29, '[]', 0, 'EUR', 'https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/rfx/rftc-50_g/share_dokumentace/en/manual_rftc-50g.pdf', '', 'https://www.elkoep.com/media/import/Elko/RFx/RFTC-50_G/3D/3d.html', '', 1769161346834, 1769161346834, '/rftc-50g                                                                                                                                                        rftc-50/g                                                                                                                                                        <p>rftc-50/g is a separate thermostat that allows wireless control of up to 4 multifunctional switching components, e.g. rfsa-6x, rfus-61, rfsti-11b-sl.</p><p>temperature measurement with the built-in sensor in the range of 0.55 ° c, temperature setting in the range of 0 to + 55 ° c in the weekly program.</p><p>the backlit lcd display displays the current and set temperature, status (on/off), battery status, day of the week, current time, etc.</p><p>battery power (2x 1.5 v aaa batteries - included in supply) with a battery life of around 1 year based on the frequency of use.</p><p>range up to 100 m (in open space), if the signal is insufficient between the controller and unit, use the signal repeater rfrp-20 or protocol component rfio2 that supports this feature.</p><p>communication frequency with bidirectional protocol rfio.</p><p>color combination of temperature unit in design of frames logus90 (plastic, glass, wood, metal, stone).</p> public visible', 'https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/rfx/rftc-50_g/share_dokumentace/en/datasheet_rftc-50g.pdf', '[{"url":"https://eshop.elkoep.com/documents/rfx/rftc-50_g/share_dokumentace/en/ec_declaration_of_conformity_rftc-50g.pdf"}]');
